    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I edited the URL with the correct label name. I'm not sure I understand what you mean @Haroenv with encoded URL.\r\n\r\nLabels are not necessary but they would be useful for:\r\n\r\n* Filtering questions coming from users not understanding our documentation (or users needing more information on a specific page)\r\n* Stats to measure how relevant our documentation becomes over time (fewer issues tagged with this label, the better it gets)\r\n\r\nIf we go that path, we should consider creating a specific label for this kind of issues.",
